+
+TOUCH2 command
+--------------
+
+touch2 <key> <exptime>\r\n
+
+Updates the expiration time of an existing item and returns the stored value
+with enough metadata to confirm the updated expiration.
+
+Response:
+  VALUE <key> <flags> <bytes>\r\n
+  <data block>\r\n
+  EXPTIME <exptime>\r\n
+  END\r\n
+
+If the item does not exist, TOUCH2 returns:
+  NOT_FOUND\r\n
